Sazka’s Chairman Ales Husak Resigns From Post, CTK Reports

-- B y   L e n k a   P o n i k e l s k a
-- 
2011-08-22T08:33:47Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-22/sazka-s-chairman-ales-husak-resigns-from-post-ctk-reports.html
Sazka AS’ Chairman Ales Husak
resigned from the post today,  CTK  reported, citing a statement
from Husak. Shareholders of the bankrupt lottery company planned
to dismiss Husak during today’s meeting, CTK said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Lenka Ponikelska in Prague at 
